Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:23.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:27.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}憎しみに　変わっていく前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:29.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何もかもそうだろ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:34.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:39.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:43.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:48.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:55.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　解り合ってたことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:57.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:00.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:05.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:11.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:16.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:23.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:26.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:30.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君はつぶやいて　信じる事が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:33.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:35.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:39.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:23.01,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛因愛而愈加沉重 卻拒絕理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:27.49,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在愛變為恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:29.59,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所有一切皆是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:34.64,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}窘迫的永遠是這眼前的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:37.46,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}彷彿被吞噬之物的寫實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:39.77,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在這被扭曲的進退兩難之時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:43.73,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使海誓山盟的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:48.08,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也漸行著冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:55.51,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}毀滅與理解之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:57.36,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}早已被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:00.89,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這難道是滅亡之盡頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:05.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}否認這一切 挺身面對之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:11.68,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即將殞落之時 都不會逃離眼前的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:16.35,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}啊，無論如何也要找尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:23.03,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的雙眸 雙手的溫存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:26.54,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}說什麼「愛總是只給我帶來傷害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:30.21,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君之低聲細語 深信之言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:33.21,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是在恐懼中哭泣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.36,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認識著軟弱 渴望著堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:39.17,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}當不再恐懼而滿懷信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:43.97,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}那將是真實的愛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:22:03.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:17.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:24.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:33.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:41.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:49.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:56.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:05.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:22:03.30,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當純真變為單純的力量 世界由此誕生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:17.84,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿透過玻璃櫥 感觸著這光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:24.94,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起的手無法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:33.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻如同墜落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:41.93,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prototype boy 拋開明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:49.42,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便無法成為傳承的美談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:56.75,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同就要失去這副身軀一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:05.92,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在極限的邊緣 跌入悲傷的深淵
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關押反政府勢力人員的設施遭到Gundam的襲擊是毋庸置疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是天行者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言說反政府勢力獨立開發了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個還只是猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼說 這都是威脅現政府的恐怖活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府為了剿滅恐怖組織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定派遣直屬治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預見了天行者的復活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並借此機會擴大A-LAWS的權限麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的主意..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是維塔的主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 差不多該我們出場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡瓦夫·裡巴爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加德薩機型已經下線了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有命令 隨時都可以出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒有這個必要 裡瓦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個作戰 已經拜託某人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪瓦恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是布林格?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然從某個角度來說 已經不屬於人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在家太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ptolemaios的修理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的新型MS的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00的TWIN DRIVE系統的調整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事還有很多喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦 不過還是不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:16.38,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯布哈利沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方… 竟然沒被聯邦發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦在非加盟國很多的中東全域撒布GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽他們說建造的目的是用粒子效果來干擾恐怖組織的聯絡網
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過實際上卻是為了妨礙中東的經濟活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:39.10,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子散佈裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓不遵從聯邦意志的國家嘗嘗苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也算托了GN粒子的福 KATARON的設施沒有被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解的真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？只是常識啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎 已確認到你們的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在打開艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救了阿扎帝斯坦的英雄機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來了真是太好了 天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們到來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看看你們的相貌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有保密義務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼不通情理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家是拔刀相助的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府組織KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們能與我們會談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是KATARON中東支部的克勞斯·古拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是天行者 自我介紹的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我理解你們的難處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們幫助了瑪麗娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我們將盡到保護她的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想呆在天行者那邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 竟然加入反政府組織
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個人想托你們保護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·庫洛斯洛特 平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 他因為被A-LAWS懷疑是KATARON的成員才牽扯進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真該說聲抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會負起責任保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這樣擅做主張…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是做好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨意跑進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算培養他們成為KATARON的成員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是保護這些沒有安身之所的孩子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦施行的片面的中東政策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其危害就以這種形式表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:06:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來因為資金所限 不能接收全部的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪麗娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 真的是瑪麗娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜大人 能陪孩子玩一會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？那麼我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是王國的象徵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該進入正題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們KATARON是為了打倒現聯邦政權…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我們並不是像你們一樣按政治的思想行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們也和聯邦是對立的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵人不是聯邦政府 而是A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和政府直屬的部隊戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我們的目的不是一致的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 為了制止A-LAWS的惡行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要聯手合作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 這裡的MS是不能和搭載GN DRIVE的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我們也想幫助你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是補給還是整備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都想助你們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.38,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波斯灣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite的損失 真是失態啊 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 給部隊丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奈金大佐 和少佐一起擔任部隊的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們A-LAWS是聯邦的矛和盾 不允許失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 今後要聽從我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎 Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我斷然拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從司令部獲得了獨自行動的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是one man army 只有一個人的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種任性的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過有許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐出動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我負責Gundam的搜索部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是作為正規軍給A-LAWS當打雜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 那傢伙還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說安德雷少尉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠實的完成著任務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是做給我看的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只做了軍人 而不是一名父親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 那件事…我想可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當大佐的養女那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細的等見面再說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是幸運的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜大人 這個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到這邊來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子也是你們的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們妄圖改變世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼也感受不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會感受不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能再次踏入那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你明白 為什麼還要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有這樣做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不指望你能瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你恨我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 希望你能接受我一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想同天行者聯合 果然還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個回答已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和A-LAWS的戰鬥一定會非常激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不遠的將來 他們與我們聯手的日子一定會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是吧 G1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們要偷懶到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快回崗位幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會談結束了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是還有一件事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露送到阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 提出無理的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能使用Gundam哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一被發現了 可能會危害到阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我使用這個機體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Gundam送回托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 你不回來也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四年間發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是天行者還是KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些挑起戰爭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能呆在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是天行者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮裡有個朋友 我想聯絡他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮還遠呢 開車去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有看到瑪麗娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還和天行者一夥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam要返回母艦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請打開升降口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意能穿越沙漠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼點準備 為什麼還在沙漠裡跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生物檢測結果出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是KATARON的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不! 我才不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還撒謊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我動粗!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的話我來問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是戰士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在軍隊呆久了所以看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目光裡並沒有戰鬥者的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 並不是KATARON的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 都發生過什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和天行者組織一同行動過的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看資料的話 你在數周之前Gundam出現的PLANT上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從事殖民衛星開發的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後現在你出現在 昨天同Gundam戰鬥過的這片區域裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 簡單的推理而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是KATARON也不是天行者的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想聽你把經過講一講
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會傷害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠洗清我身上的嫌疑麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會盡力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四宇宙艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拉克·齊寧大尉同屬下5人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 那是真的麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上送去指令書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個天真的女人的話會壞了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了KATARON的軍事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是很可能Gundam也在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上採取對應措施
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 請也給我們出擊許可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別硬來 先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明Gundam也在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這指令書是什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要使用自走機械人的Kill-Mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行這種非人道的作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層部的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份作戰的內容 閣下什麼都感覺不到麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然感覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是反政府勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有給予同情的必要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進行這種作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐反對轉屬到這裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉誤解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米盧諾夫大佐這個人為了任務的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是連骨肉之親都能夠捨棄的男人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連骨肉之親都…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人眼睜睜看著母親死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS知道了反政府組織的位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊來和提艾利亞進行聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混賬!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說過讓你報告給A-LAWS了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是我們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出判斷的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛斯洛特君 現在馬上從這裡逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS得知了你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙是在法律之上行動的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的權限保護不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我的存在被知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道… 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從王留美發來的緊急加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎正在向KATARON的設施進發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 張開對衛星光學迷彩 緊急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行Gundam的出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密號 緊急上浮開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離海面剩餘時間0043
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被A-LAWS發現了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那裡還有小孩子在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的MS隊來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來摧毀這裡的麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的數量是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡得知基地的情報的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 是天行者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點吧孩子們帶到掩體裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯 出擊吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰力差別太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加強防禦 等待天行者的救援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟炸麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視線確認懷疑為敵方基地的建築物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方MS出現!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用那種舊型的MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉入掃蕩敵方基地的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自走機械人 射出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自走機械人 射出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍用自走機械人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 隱蔽!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲了一步麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的人們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給你們了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯機 去迎擊先行的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種動作!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 迎擊Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先行告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道 為什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是… 這他媽是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人做的事情麼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用無人兵器進行的虐殺行為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連扳機都不自己扣下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連罪惡感都不打算承擔麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙射炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.50,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1008)}Double Bazooka
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.71,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1008)}Burst Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初期目標已經完成 撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饒不了你們! A-LAWS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別他媽給我逃啊 A-LAWS!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是… A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 我們的死敵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵 為了戰鬥的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的我卻渴望得到正常人的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那樣做的懲罰麼? 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我告訴了他們才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上 就到阿扎帝斯坦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 阿扎帝斯坦會…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種規模 不是恐怖襲擊什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那個顏色是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜對了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去不返的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去不返的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去不返的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無一不揪扯著什麼人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為後悔的隱痛 陣陣襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:21:05.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:16.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:25.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:38.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:21:05.54,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prototype boy 拋開明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:16.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便無法成為傳承的美談
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:25.86,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同就要失去這副身軀一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:38.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在極限的邊緣 跌入悲傷的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.29,EDcn,,0000,0000,0000,,

